ficant impact on quality of life and potential for exacerbation.\n- Immediate referral to a neurologist or ophthalmologist specializing in neuromuscular disorders is recommended for further evaluation and management.\n\n---\n\n**2. CLINICAL PRESENTATION**\n\nThe patient's clinical presentation includes a detailed symptom analysis focusing on the drooping eyelids (ptosis), which fluctuate in severity and improve with rest. The patient has reported these symptoms for 5 days, with no significant change in severity over this period. The fluctuating nature of the symptoms and	["textual_to_followup", "followup_only"]	"workflow_complete"	{"final_confidence": 0.8, "average_confidence": 0.5}	2025-08-05 10:39:53.939179+00	2025-08-05 10:39:53.939179+00
